{"tid":31752,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人同自己兄弟姐妹性格完全唔似？","createTime":"2016-12-09T23:09:47.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T06:04:24.000Z","uid":56139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d1059b2ae669a312d3078e9602b2a70645df4615","tid":31752,"uid":56139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T23:09:47.000Z","msg":"我同我阿哥超級唔似<br />\n樣完全唔似已經唔洗講<br />\n性格方面 我好被動 阿哥好主動<br />\n佢超多朋友 whatsapp成日響 相反我部手機響就係通知我遊戲體力滿左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/poison.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢亦都好多生活圈子 追星又有 同事又有 讀書又有 已經數唔到 相反我得一兩個朋友only <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有次電腦開住網頁版whatsapp 比佢見到我個whatsapp無人搵 係到串我無朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時懷疑自己真係屋企人執翻黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申我94年 我哥92年 我同我哥就好似光同暗既正反面<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實我都係想呻下only<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fcc58027053d5785d1c9bb5152d282700e24d06","tid":31752,"uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T23:18:11.000Z","msg":"有個無講嘢近十幾年嘅&quot;阿哥&quot;<br />\n話就話住埋一齊，但係喺屋企只會各自各修行"},{"pid":"7f5f2a8f4ad8056cebc8c95e7695ed8b2a9a0884","tid":31752,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T23:24:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dfb52c34c68778e5981a6ee43af4f888350ba453","tid":31752,"uid":56139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T23:42:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有個無講嘢近十幾年嘅&quot;阿哥&quot;<br />\n話就話住埋一齊，但係喺屋企只會各自各修行</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n各有各用電腦<br />\n我同我哥同一間房 叫住有翻啲交流 巴打慘過我"},{"pid":"7182f48c8bde8a409924d861b7197974a14a5a67","tid":31752,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T00:10:13.000Z","msg":"因為主動哩家野一個就夠，由細都大你都慣左呀哥會主動"},{"pid":"f7d12f4e2441d33ecc7eef411b0b4edaeedac172","tid":31752,"uid":56139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"